The evidence with the title 'PolitiFact: only 2 in 1,000 pay 'death tax' Trump wants to repeal? ' says Oct 27, 2017  ... PolitiFact : do only 2 in 1,000 'ultra wealthy' pay 'death tax' that Trump wants  ... That what Republicans call the " death tax " is the estate tax "on the ultra wealthy," which , in 2016, was paid by only "two out of every 1,000 people.". 
